message.content: It is difficult to generalize the interests and obsessions of all children in Kashmir, as individuals have diverse preferences and passions regardless of their geographical location. However, like children anywhere else in the world, some common interests among kids in Kashmir might include technology, video games, social media, sports, music, fashion, and popular culture. It's important to remember that these interests can vary significantly from child to child, and there are also many young individuals in Kashmir who prioritize education, art, community involvement, and other enriching activities.
